i think that's agreed upon...<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Not all mages like chaining pets.  For example, with a poor or low data rate connection, like a modem, chaining may be much more risk than it is worth.  Some non-epicked mages prefer to get and keep a single good pet.  Until the upgrade to the GV line, a DSing MS pet was a legitimate choice.  Still is, for mages 50-52.<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Calebe:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  For Chroma's try this. <br>
