EM isn't that good. It doesn't do 717 damage. There was a nerf to dotting a long time ago that made any mob moving while dotted taking 66% damage per tick from the dot. So a 100pt dot would do 66pts of damage if the mob was moving the entire time. Now that has been removed and dots do full damage regardless if a mob is moving. Dots never did 1/3 more damage if a mob wasn't moving they just did full damage. <br>
<br>
Also EM and MoE break root. They have a DD component at the begining of them so it is a nuke with a dot component so it can break root. If you redo your calculations you will see that the dots are worthless lol. Because a mage with focus bracer and items can make SoS do 990dd while a mage with focus items will still get the same 800damage from MoE. Just like a mage using SoSwords could get it to do over 700dd with focus bracer a mage using EM will only do 600dd.<br>
<br>
